text: Fumio Takashina (born 1911, date of death unknown) was a Japanese diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Japanese male divers Category:Olympic divers of Japan Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
